{"tid":360143,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"前騎師鄭雨滇被追744萬","createTime":"2017-08-15T05:05:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-15T05:05:45.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e6431f98012d259733324dd596bc1389651f4ffe","tid":360143,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T05:05:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20122080&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170815\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20122080%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170815&d=aQcvaE3XEPnkTHhprgLkApWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=4e67d372\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20122080%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170815&h=28bf6dfe\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20122080&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170815</a><br />\n<br />\n前騎師鄭雨滇被追744萬<br />\n<br />\n法庭&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170815/large/15ls3p01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170815%2Flarge%2F15ls3p01.jpg&h=571c80c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鄭雨滇月前遭撤銷騎師資格。<br />\n資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】月前遭撤銷騎師資格的前華人騎師一哥鄭雨滇被指欠債，遭財務公司入稟高院連本帶利追討744萬元。原告迅興信貸有限公司指鄭與女子勞狄欣於2015年8月共同借款605萬元，去年3月另簽還款協議，惟兩人未按協議還款。原告另向鄭追討一筆個人借貸約10萬元。&nbsp;<br />\n鄭雨滇（36歲）於1999年出道，2007至2008年度曾贏42場頭馬，京奧時任港區火炬接力手。上年他先後因策騎時未盡全力、拒向馬會提供財務紀錄，及向第三者透露馬匹狀況而被罰停賽，今年4月遭馬會牌照委員會釘牌。<br />\n案件編號：HCA1893/17<br />\n■記者勞東來"}]}